  </sponsors>
  <source>Merck Sharp &amp; Dohme Corp.</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study will estimate the effects of rolofylline, alone and in addition to loop diuretic
      therapy on pulmonary capillary wedge pressure and other hemodynamic parameters, in patients
      with heart failure and renal impairment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
